CBZ Holdings Ltd. (CBZ)  received a $60
million loan from the  Eastern and Southern Trade Development
Bank  to help boost lending to customers, the Daily News
reported, citing the development bank.  CBZ will use $20 million of the loan to provide mortgages
in  Zimbabwe , the Harare-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
